{"tid":409502,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我隻貓係咪有咗","createTime":"2017-09-22T06:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T19:02:44.000Z","uid":41131,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e390259db86869300b237e1045caba2813cd683","tid":409502,"uid":41131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:03:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我屋企有三隻貓（一隻仔10歲無痷、一隻仔1歲幾痷咗、一隻女未夠半歲未痷）<br />\n因為10歲嗰隻好驚出街，之前屋企又得佢一隻，所以就無痷到。<br />\n女仔嗰隻收養咗個幾月，已經諗住盡早幫佢絕育，但尋晚同佢瞓見到佢粒pink lin大咗，一google就見到貓女有咗粒lin會大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無黃貓主人可以睇下咁係咪正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/140217_54fe65ffa2be95f67b51efea9ac839b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F140217_54fe65ffa2be95f67b51efea9ac839b7.jpg&h=9d24ee50&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/140218_54fe65ffa2be95f67b51efea9ac839b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F140218_54fe65ffa2be95f67b51efea9ac839b7.jpg&h=45a98bf8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6b3c37871a02bd49dbbe03298064b42d30a2f65","tid":409502,"uid":37389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:05:45.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"></span></span>"},{"pid":"79e2a95741cea9372bd5494be2616caa30c53a52","tid":409502,"uid":149236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ed65e675e079d642780f1eeb637f4bf9964c1e","tid":409502,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a151a671d3430bf97faf5138cddffa58604